### Personal Protection Equipment

### So you're caring for someone with Covid

Where possible, follow the guidance from public health authorities. Recent guidance from [WHO](https://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/handle/10665/331215/WHO-2019-nCov-IPCPPE_use-2020.1-eng.pdf) and the [CDC](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/infection-control/control-recommendations.html) includes the following: 

* **Medical mask, preferably N95** (20-30 EUR/USD) ([example](https://www.amazon.de/dp/B085H6Y6HN/ref=sr_1_22?keywords=n95&qid=1584011653&sr=8-22))
* **Gown** (5 EUR/USD) ([example](https://www.amazon.de/dp/B00FRGIS56/ref=sr_1_5?keywords=medizinischer+Schutzkittel&qid=1584012077&sr=8-5))
* **Gloves** (10-15 EUR/USD) ([example](https://www.amazon.de/dp/B01LWJ80C7/ref=sr_1_8?crid=3J837JBVX0LC4&keywords=handschuhe+schutz&qid=1584011916&sprefix=gloves%2Caps%2C204&sr=8-8))
* **Eye protection** (4 EUR/USD) ([example](https://www.amazon.de/dp/B002THV25Y/ref=sr_1_5?keywords=augenschutz&qid=1584011828&sr=8-5))
